narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: If you're interested in fixed income trading or finance in general, take this class. Don't take for an easy Econ credit.
Very interesting lectures, very hard tests.
Yes because you learn useful stuff
I would recommend the class because you learn a lot and the grading system is not too harsh.
It is a good overview of financial topics - gives a great intro to topics that are relevant if you are going into finance as a career.
